Card

Class MoveToLocationCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • Card.Card
      • Card.MoveToLocationCard

  • public class MoveToLocationCard
extends Card
    This class is for cards that force the player to move to a specific location. Some of these cards have special modifiers like changes in the rate owed and if the player gets money for passing go.
